<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1330,1631]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">
Gravenhorst compared this species with 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[583,991,1330,1353]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis box="[583,829,1330,1353]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[929,983,1330,1353]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[1043,1432,1330,1353]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Perapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marchicum">
<emphasis box="[1043,1267,1330,1353]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Perapion marchicum</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[1367,1424,1330,1353]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Despite its very short original description, body sheen and dimension (“nicht völlig eine Linie lang”, and therefore less than 
<quantity box="[211,347,1400,1423]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.25" metricValueMax="2.3" metricValueMin="2.2" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="2.25" valueMax="2.3" valueMin="2.2">2.2–2.3 mm</quantity>
long) suggest 
<taxonomicName box="[525,677,1400,1423]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis box="[525,677,1400,1423]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion chloris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be conspecific with 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[963,1396,1400,1423]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis box="[963,1216,1400,1423]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[1331,1388,1400,1423]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
. In accordance, a specimen of 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[443,854,1434,1457]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis box="[443,690,1434,1457]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[792,846,1434,1457]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
is here designated as the 
<typeStatus box="[1133,1217,1434,1457]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">neotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[1255,1360,1434,1457]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis box="[1255,1360,1434,1457]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">A. chloris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It is a male (fig. 
<number box="[260,274,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="2.0">2</number>
) labelled: Umg. Berl.: Buch, Coll, Beck / 
<typeStatus box="[723,844,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">NEOTYPE</typeStatus>
<taxonomicName authority="Gravenhorst, 1807" authorityName="Gravenhorst" authorityYear="1807" box="[851,1202,1469,1492]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis box="[851,995,1469,1492]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion chloris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gravenhorst" box="[1001,1202,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" refString="Gravenhorst, I. L. C. (1807) Vergleichende Uebersicht des Linneischen und einiger neuern zoologischen Systeme, nebst dem eigeschalteten Verzeichnisse der zoologischen Sammlungen des Verfassers und den Beschreibungen neuer Thierarten, die in derselben vorhanden sind. Dieterich, Gottingen, XX + 476 pp." type="book" year="1807">
Gravenhorst, 
<number box="[1146,1202,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1807.0">1807</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, C. Giusto des. 
<number box="[1369,1422,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="2015.0">2015</number>
/ 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[151,561,1504,1527]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis box="[151,396,1504,1527]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[496,553,1504,1527]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
, det. C. Giusto, 
<number box="[732,789,1504,1527]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="2015.0">2015</number>
. Measurements: body length: 
<quantity box="[1108,1205,1504,1527]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.04" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="2.04">2.04 mm</quantity>
, Lr: 
<quantity box="[1255,1352,1504,1527]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.4" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="0.44">0.44 mm</quantity>
, Wmsr: 
<quantity box="[151,248,1538,1561]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="0.15">0.15 mm</quantity>
, Lp: 
<quantity box="[303,400,1538,1561]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.2" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="0.42">0.42 mm</quantity>
, Wp: 
<quantity box="[463,560,1538,1561]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.699999999999999" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="0.47">0.47 mm</quantity>
, Le: 
<quantity box="[613,711,1538,1561]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.42" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="1.42">1.42 mm</quantity>
, We: 
<quantity box="[770,869,1538,1561]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.7" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="0.87">0.87 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1330,1631]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">
